rows.label: tlk42300011_05_msg0001
rows.name:
When Alst become more peaceful,
Limuli probably switch job to salvager.

rows.label: tlk42300011_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Would like to switch job now,
but Gegebi tell Limuli no.

rows.label: tlk42300011_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Seem like Gegebi like Limuli more
than Limuli thought.

rows.label: tlk42300011_05_msg0004
rows.name:
So Limuli OK with staying around
little while longer.
